OL,3,CPensioner sentenced after Scarlett
OL,4,CRossborough crash death
OL,6,FA 92-year-old Co Antrim man who
OL,7,Fknocked down and killed schoolgirl
OL,8,FScarlett Rossborough has been
OL,9,Fsentenced for a charge of causing her
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FJohn Noble Lindsay was handed a
OL,13,Fsentence of ten months, which was
OL,14,Fsuspended for 12 months, at Belfast
OL,15,FCrown Court on Friday.
OL,17,FDue to his ailing health Lindsay, from
OL,18,FPrince Andrew Way in Carrickfergus,
OL,19,Fwas excused from appeared in person
OL,20,Fand he attended his sentence hearing
OL,21,Fvia a videolink.
