OL,6,FAs Scarlett's family sat in the public
OL,7,Fgallery, Judge Patricia Smyth paid
OL,8,Ftribute to the eight-year old who was
OL,9,Fstruck and killed as she walked along
OL,10,FHigh Street in Carrick on the morning
OL,11,Fof August 9, 2023.
OL,13,FJudge Smyth also endorsed calls by the
OL,14,Fchild's family regarding the proposed
OL,15,F'Scarlett's Law' which seeks a change
OL,16,Fin legislation regarding very elderly
OL,17,Fdrivers in the interests of public
OL,18,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
