OL,6,FScarlett - who attended Linn Primary
OL,7,FSchool in Larne - was amongst a group
OL,8,Fof children and adult leaders from a
OL,9,Flocal community centre summer scheme
OL,10,Fenjoying a day out to Carrick Castle.
OL,12,FIn the moments before the fatal
OL,13,Fcollision, Lindsay had parked his car
OL,14,Fin a disabled parking space.
OL,16,FAfter initially parking his car,
OL,17,FLindsay was captured on CCTV exiting
OL,18,Fthe vehicle then getting back into the
OL,19,Fcar. He then attempted to re-park the
OL,20,Fcar and began moving the vehicle
OL,21,Fbackwards and forwards several times.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
