OL,6,FAs the group was walking along the
OL,7,Ffootpath on High Street, Lindsay's car
OL,8,Fmounted the pavement and struck three
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,FAt the point of impact, Lindsay's car
OL,12,Fwas travelling between 11 and 13 mph
OL,13,Fand the court heard 'pedal
OL,14,Fmisapplication' could have been a
OL,15,Fpossible cause of the collision, as
OL,16,Fcould confusion on Lindsay's part.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
