OL,4,CRossborough crash death
OL,6,FWhilst two of the youngsters were
OL,7,Fthrown into the doorway of a shop and
OL,8,Fdidn't suffer any serious injury,
OL,9,FScarlett was trapped between the rear
OL,10,Fof Lindsay's car and the wall of an
OL,11,Fadjacent building.
OL,13,FIn the direct aftermath, members of
OL,14,Fthe public rushed to help and
OL,15,Fsignalled for Lindsay to move his car
OL,16,Fforward and both the PSNI and
OL,17,FAmbulance Service attended the scene.
OL,19,FDue to the catastrophic injuries that
OL,20,Fshe sustained, Scarlett could not be
OL,21,Fsaved.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
