OL,6,FDuring today's sentencing, Judge Smyth
OL,7,Fsaid: "The enormity of that tragedy
OL,8,Fcannot be put into words.
OL,10,F"Scarlett was described as the
OL,11,Fprincess of the family. She was the
OL,12,Fkindest, most sensitive, empathetic
OL,13,Flittle person.
OL,15,F"She was determined and she was
OL,16,Fpassionate. She was such a talented
OL,17,Flittle girl.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
