OL,3,CPensioner sentenced after Scarlett
OL,4,CRossborough crash death
OL,6,F"Scarlett was a little girl who had a
OL,7,Fbusiness head on her shoulders. She
OL,8,Fhad plans for her future. She saw
OL,9,Fherself owning an apartment in New
OL,10,FYork."
OL,12,FJudge Smyth spoke of Scarlett's love
OL,13,Fof sports, music and art and how much
OL,14,Fshe adored spending time with her
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,FShe continued: "Scarlett's home was a
OL,18,Fvery happy place. There were pizza
OL,19,Fnights and movie nights, they spent
OL,20,Ftime together as an ordinary family
OL,21,F... and how precious that time is now.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
