OL,6,F"Now there's just an empty chair when
OL,7,Fthe family sits down."
OL,9,FSaying all Scarlett's family "has
OL,10,Fsuffered and continues to suffer",
OL,11,FJudge Smyth spoke of how her mother
OL,12,F"has counted the days she had with her
OL,13,Flittle daughter - 3,243 days" and how
OL,14,Fshe has been left "haunted by the
OL,15,Fdetails of this tragedy, as any mother
OL,16,Fwould be."
OL,18,FShe added Scarlett's father's life has
OL,19,Fbeen "ripped apart" and he has
OL,20,Fstruggled to comprehend how he lost
OL,21,Fhis daughter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
