OL,6,FSaying Scarlett "left her mark on all
OL,7,Fwho met her", the Judge also spoke of
OL,8,Fa tree which stands as a permanent
OL,9,Fmemory to the "beautiful child that
OL,10,Fshe was."
OL,12,FAddressing Scarlett's loved ones, the
OL,13,FBelfast Recorder told them that no
OL,14,Fsentence she passed could bring them
OL,15,Fany comfort or make any difference to
OL,16,Fthe grief they felt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
