OL,6,FShe said: "I accept that you are
OL,7,Fdevastated by what happened. The
OL,8,Fshocking circumstances of her death
OL,9,Faffected so many people and there is
OL,10,Fnothing that can turn back the clock
OL,11,Fand restore the precious young life
OL,12,Fthat has been lost."
OL,14,FJudge Smyth then spoke to Lindsay - a
OL,15,Fformer RUC officer - via the videolink
OL,16,Fand told him "I recognise that you
OL,17,Fhave been devastated by causing
OL,18,FScarlett's death but that you also
OL,19,Frecognise that how you feel counts for
OL,20,Fnothing in comparison to what her
OL,21,Fparents and her family are suffering."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
