OL,6,FAcknowledging that prior to the fatal
OL,7,Fcollision Lindsay had been driving for
OL,8,F72 years and had a completely clear
OL,9,Fdriving record, the Judge revealed
OL,10,Fthat he surrendered his licence the
OL,11,Fday after he killed Scarlett.
OL,13,FShe also accepted Lindsay was a
OL,14,F"frail" and "very sick man" with a
OL,15,Frange of health issues and who has a
OL,16,Flife expectancy of between nine months
OL,17,Fand a year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
