OL,6,FBranding the case as "exceptional",
OL,7,FJudge Smyth said she had taken into
OL,8,Faccount Lindsay's ill health, his
OL,9,F"extreme" age, his "previous
OL,10,Funblemished character" and his plea to
OL,11,Fthe charge.
OL,13,FImposed the sentence which she
OL,14,Fsuspended "as an act of mercy", Judge
OL,15,FSmyth also disqualified Lindsay from
OL,16,Fdriving for 12 months.
